title: Week 11 Picks Against the Spread, Best Bets, Gambling Advice (Football 11/15)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Pete Prisco and R.J. White for Week 11 gambling advice, covering all 13 games on Sunday and Monday. The guys discuss Texans-Ravens (5:00), Chiefs-Chargers (10:50), Jags-Colts (14:20), Bears-Rams (21:20), Saints-Bucs (26:45), Dolphins-Bills (29:50), Pats-Eagles (42:10), Cowboys-Lions (46:20), Falcons-Panthers (47:10), Broncos-Vikings (51:30), Jets-Redskins (53:30), Cardinals-49ers (57:00) and Bengals-Raiders (59:15).
 
To learn more about listener data and our privacy practices visit: https://www.audacyinc.com/privacy-policy
